# Memory

{{#if name}}{{name}}, this{{else}}This{{/if}} is where your assistant captures things you tell it - preferences, corrections, project state, who's who. Each note has a type:

- **user** - facts about you (role, timezone, knowledge)
- **feedback** - corrections + things you've told the assistant to keep doing
- **project** - time-bound work state (deadlines, releases, in-flight)
- **reference** - pointers to external systems (dashboards, channels, files)

Open the graph view in Obsidian to see them clustered by type. Search by `#memory` tag to see everything captured.

